text: Julien Bogaert (18 August 1924 - 3 October 2018) was a Belgian sprint canoeist. He competed in the late 1940s. He was eliminated in the K-1 1000 m event at the 1948 Summer Olympics in London. Bogaert died on 3 October 2018 in Brussels, Belgium at the age of 94. ==References== ==Other websites== *Julien Bogaert's profile at Sports Reference.com Category:1924 births Category:2018 deaths Category:Olympians for Belgium Category:Canoeists
